social_posts.post_text: Old San Juan was a total vibe. Our trip to Puerto Rico was incredible. It was the closest thing to a vacation we’ve felt this year. Evelyn loved the music, salsa dancing and all the different spices. Can’t wait to go back! Hasta luego Puerto Rico you’ve captured our hearts.

Sixty love filled days we had the honor of being a part of in 2022. A common theme it seems…veils & sails. Looking back through our teams favorite images was full of so many emotions. Last year was one of our biggest as a team and the most full personally. It takes a village to get over a mountain of images. From the photography day, to the editing, album design printing, blogging, communicating, planning, and then there’s the home front with Grammys/nanny/aunties helping with Evey so I could show up to you. I couldn’t have done it without this village. I think we have learned so much from 2022 and become even more sensitive to our why as a company. Cheers to 2023!! 

#flashback #weddingfavorites #bestofweddings #cfpwedding #weddingphotography #weddingphotographer #annapoliswedding #baltimorewedding

The fourth trimester is something very few people talk about. It is a real time period that needs more space. After experiencing it myself I realize our village needs to surround new families with warmth, love and nourishment. My village helped lift me up in the midst of my busiest work season and amazing but challenging shifts in our life. They need warm soups, showers, quiet moments to breath and your love. This new momma and baby boy embody this feeling for me. They just need the seconds of peace together to calibrate to life on the outside together. Together. In this stillness the peacefulness felt is amplified by the tribe that is there to uplift and carry them to the next phase ✨💛 

Be patient with yourselves parents. You are everything this new soul needs…welcome to the world baby boy you are in amazing hands

One of my personal habits is arriving crazy early to my events. Especially when it’s over the bay bridge. Today I’m at @kentislandresort Come with me on a lil venue tour of their new evolving and beautiful property!

Thank you for an amazing time capturing you two and all you do for our country. #usnawedding #navywedding #cfpassociate #cfpwedding #annapoliswedding #autographhotels

Hanging in Eastport for an engagement session today and couldn’t help but reminisce back to these sweet two. Anyone know where this secret beach is?!

I am on sick leave until friday. 

I am feeling like a human today but was in the ER until midnight. I’m recovering at home and thankful my wife forced me to go get fluid, zofran & pain meds. My family would not let me work or touch my computer today so I can HEAL. It has been clear the last three days  many of my clients forget I’m a human. I’m a one woman show with three amazing photographers who shoot with me. I answer all emails calls, I edit, cull, backup, prepare for the following weekends for a team of four of us shooters. I also photograph at least 3-5 families and couples each week. I run a studio and rent said studio out. I design your albums, order them and quality check them. I love what I do with a passion. A PASSION. I will never do something that impacts quality and my expectations.. I am a wife and mother on top of my professional titles. 

….But I will not be treated like a computer!!!!!!

Please remember people you email aren’t the computer we are sitting in our own lives doing our best too. ✨💛✨

 Wedding vendors are humans who don’t have a HR Customer service team to cover for them or answer phones when they are ill. Please give me grace as I heal soo I can be a rockstar for my amazing couple this weekend. Thank you ✌🏻💛✨

Just a lil fun with Evelyn’s neighborhood girl squad. 🫶🏼pretty girls walk like this ✌🏻Evenings have changed for the better watching her grow and make lil friend connections.

When I walked through their door, I got all of the feels. I captured them engaged, married, and now they are parents🥺. My eyes welled up. I was frozen in that moment looking at them holding their baby girl. I realized it was one of those golden moments in my life. Those flashes of joy and experiences you know will be a memory you keep with you. I feel soo honored to be the person to capture these milestones especially in this sweet families life. Baby El🥲 you are strong beautiful and one lucky little girl. Y ✨💛
